name: AnyInfectionPriorToAnesthesiaConceptsSNOMEDCT
title: Any Infection Prior to Anesthesia Concepts SNOMED CT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values identifies patients who have preoperative documentation of an infection.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have preoperative documentation of an infection.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent select infections. Codes used are to be SNOMED-CT codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude for fungal infections, viral infections and infections that are not documented as current or active.)
